# Maven wrapper (keep config but ignore binary JAR if preferred, though some commit it)
# By default, maven-wrapper.jar can be checked in or ignored. Let's ignore it to keep repo clean,
# or we can allow it. Usually maven-wrapper.jar is ignored by some, but standard Spring Boot templates commit it.
